1
00:00:00,531 --> 00:00:05,055
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,055 --> 00:00:10,559
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,559 --> 00:00:16,987
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,987 --> 00:00:21,467
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,467 --> 00:00:25,915
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,915 --> 00:00:30,826
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,826 --> 00:00:34,875
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,875 --> 00:00:39,410
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:43,707
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,707 --> 00:00:48,472
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,472 --> 00:00:51,963
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,963 --> 00:00:55,643
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,289 --> 00:01:00,667
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,667 --> 00:01:03,040
=Episode 2=

15
00:01:06,944 --> 00:01:10,300
(I won the world championship abroad
in mixed martial arts.)

16
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:14,100
(Due to an ankle injury,
I had to leave the ring)

17
00:01:14,432 --> 00:01:17,500
(and came back home
to look for opportunities.)

18
00:01:17,952 --> 00:01:21,440
(When I got home,
I found out my twin sister)

19
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:23,533
(was treated unfairly in her company.)

20
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:26,464
(She got slapped
and suffered a mild concussion.)

21
00:01:27,008 --> 00:01:31,633
(So, my sister developed hypersomnia.
The company paid compensation.)

22
00:01:31,904 --> 00:01:34,633
(She got 40 days of paid leave.)

23
00:01:34,633 --> 00:01:37,933
(She's gradually getting better.)

24
00:01:38,272 --> 00:01:40,533
(However, she's suffering mentally.)

25
00:01:41,312 --> 00:01:45,333
(Her vacation is going to end.
I persuaded her to change jobs,)

26
00:01:45,728 --> 00:01:46,666
(but she refused,)

27
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:50,333
(because joining WE Group is her dream.)

28
00:01:50,333 --> 00:01:52,966
(So, I made a bold decision.)

29
00:01:52,966 --> 00:01:55,533
(I dressed as my sister
and went to work.)

30
00:01:55,533 --> 00:01:59,300
(I'll make those
who bullied my sister pay a price.)

31
00:02:20,233 --> 00:02:21,632
Miss Jin!

32
00:02:24,096 --> 00:02:25,312
(My neck...)

33
00:02:27,264 --> 00:02:28,600
(It doesn't hurt now.)

34
00:02:30,266 --> 00:02:33,600
The meeting for the new product
is about to start. The executives are here.

35
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:37,133
Alright.

36
00:02:38,666 --> 00:02:39,600
Go to the meeting.

37
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:46,366
Miss Jin, hurry up. They're all here.

38
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:51,488
All of them?
I'll fight them all at once.

39
00:03:17,933 --> 00:03:20,000
Who will present the new proposal later?

40
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:23,400
Anyway, it's not me.
I'm always nervous in front of Lan Chen.

41
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:27,966
He was voted the Top One
for Hubus Under 30 at such a young age.

42
00:03:28,466 --> 00:03:31,433
Lan Chen is picky.
Let's see what will happen.

43
00:03:40,866 --> 00:03:43,100
Hello, Mr. Lan.

44
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:43,968
Sit down.

45
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:02,200
Everyone, our new product
uses unique Tyroca seeds

46
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:08,033
from the Tianshan Mountains
at 37 degrees north latitude.

47
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:12,600
The extracted antioxidant matter
is as high as 78 percent...

48
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,304
63.4 percent.

49
00:04:15,666 --> 00:04:19,966
Well, why did I say 78 percent?

50
00:04:19,966 --> 00:04:23,333
After Tyroca seeds are dried,
washed, and purified,

51
00:04:23,766 --> 00:04:27,900
0.25 grams of the antioxidant factor
attached to the surface will be lost,

52
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:34,400
which is a decrease of 14.6 percent,
so only 63.4 percent is left.

53
00:04:37,833 --> 00:04:42,100
Mr. Lan is right,
but as the creative director,

54
00:04:42,666 --> 00:04:46,733
I have an idea. Our product has passion.

55
00:04:47,166 --> 00:04:49,733
It does not represent merely data.

56
00:04:49,733 --> 00:04:51,600
It's just business.

57
00:04:54,066 --> 00:04:56,700
There is no need
for passion in business.

58
00:04:58,066 --> 00:05:02,733
All we do is to make the market
need our products.

59
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,733
I see, Mr. Lan.

60
00:05:05,866 --> 00:05:09,933
Accelerate research progress.
We need money from Lihuai International.

61
00:05:10,566 --> 00:05:11,866
Do it quickly.

62
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,333
Yes, Mr. Lan.

63
00:05:27,266 --> 00:05:29,033
What happened?

64
00:05:30,633 --> 00:05:32,933
I was accidentally hit
by a car this morning.

65
00:05:35,033 --> 00:05:36,000
I hit him.

66
00:05:36,533 --> 00:05:37,566
I was in his car.

67
00:05:38,866 --> 00:05:39,733
Alright.

68
00:05:41,933 --> 00:05:44,533
You guys can receive ten times of
medical expenses and consolation money.

69
00:05:45,433 --> 00:05:46,533
Let's get this over.

70
00:05:48,233 --> 00:05:51,933
You guys can leave, except Miss Jin.

71
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,000
Miss Jin.

72
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,633
Do you want to continue this job?

73
00:06:16,433 --> 00:06:18,533
If you still want to be my secretary,

74
00:06:19,166 --> 00:06:21,200
please don't be impulsive again.

75
00:06:21,433 --> 00:06:22,233
I...

76
00:06:23,433 --> 00:06:25,233
You know how you got this job.

77
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:29,566
I went against their advice
to make you my secretary.

78
00:06:30,466 --> 00:06:34,100
Since you chose this job,
you have to be responsible.

79
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:44,600
Send me today's schedule. Buy me
macarons. Don't get the flavor wrong.

80
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:47,566
Put them on my desk in 15 minutes.

81
00:06:48,366 --> 00:06:49,166
Humph.

82
00:07:00,066 --> 00:07:02,560
Miss, please line up over there.

83
00:07:08,032 --> 00:07:13,761
(Ten minutes later)

84
00:07:20,466 --> 00:07:21,300
Here you are.

85
00:07:23,233 --> 00:07:24,033
Thank you.

86
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:26,900
Hey.

87
00:07:29,533 --> 00:07:30,700
Why didn't you queue?

88
00:07:32,366 --> 00:07:34,600
He has reserved them in advance.

89
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,433
And this is the last box.

90
00:07:36,733 --> 00:07:38,400
You can try a new flavor.

91
00:07:39,264 --> 00:07:40,928
The last box?

92
00:07:41,866 --> 00:07:43,966
I'll give it to you in this case.

93
00:07:45,866 --> 00:07:47,933
I think you need it more than I do.

94
00:07:49,466 --> 00:07:51,200
Thanks. How much do I owe you?

95
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:54,000
No problem. You can pay me next time.

96
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,400
Thank you.

97
00:07:58,066 --> 00:08:00,666
Can I order that flavor?

98
00:08:00,666 --> 00:08:03,500
Sure, Mr. Zeng.
We will make it for you right away.

99
00:08:05,233 --> 00:08:08,033
Hey, Miss Jin.

100
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,200
Do you think
you can do whatever you want

101
00:08:11,433 --> 00:08:13,233
because Mr. Lan backs you up?

102
00:08:13,233 --> 00:08:15,333
You didn't learn a thing from that slap?

103
00:08:16,366 --> 00:08:17,933
Are you a fool?

104
00:08:19,433 --> 00:08:20,966
Be smart.

105
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,033
It was you?

106
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:30,333
She became a moron.

107
00:08:44,266 --> 00:08:45,733
Show some respect, you two.

108
00:08:46,033 --> 00:08:47,933
Don't upset Miss Jin anymore.

109
00:08:50,866 --> 00:08:52,566
You better learn a lesson.

110
00:08:53,266 --> 00:08:56,033
The man who hits a woman is the worst.

111
00:09:08,033 --> 00:09:11,600
Find Ling Feng from the Muay Thai gym
to teach her a harsh lesson.

112
00:09:11,933 --> 00:09:12,933
Who is Ling Feng?

113
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:20,233
Treat your colleagues well,
and don't underestimate women.

114
00:09:20,433 --> 00:09:22,100
Or else I can do it again.

115
00:09:37,533 --> 00:09:39,633
My appetite is gone. You eat them.

116
00:09:41,733 --> 00:09:45,600
What's wrong with you?
Don't waste my time again.

117
00:09:49,833 --> 00:09:50,900
Well,

118
00:09:51,466 --> 00:09:52,700
you've been away for a month.

119
00:09:53,266 --> 00:09:54,766
Let's review the work.

120
00:09:57,766 --> 00:10:00,933
First, the development of new product.

121
00:10:01,233 --> 00:10:04,233
This is the best way
to be invested by Lihuai International.

122
00:10:04,666 --> 00:10:05,600
Second...

123
00:10:09,533 --> 00:10:10,333
Miss Jin.

124
00:10:11,936 --> 00:10:13,400
Did you notice anything?

125
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,200
What?

126
00:10:15,666 --> 00:10:16,833
My tie is crooked.

127
00:10:17,066 --> 00:10:17,933
So what?

128
00:10:18,466 --> 00:10:19,500
Help me fix it.

129
00:10:20,533 --> 00:10:22,366
What's wrong with you?

130
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:24,000
Can't you do it yourself?

131
00:10:25,733 --> 00:10:27,700
It's what you should do as a secretary.

132
00:10:27,866 --> 00:10:28,799
Since you chose this job...

133
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,000
Fine, I will help you.

134
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:44,139
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

135
00:10:44,139 --> 00:10:48,417
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

136
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:53,233
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪

137
00:10:53,233 --> 00:10:55,166
Ahem.

138
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,824
Mom.

139
00:11:00,466 --> 00:11:03,433
Miss Jin, you may leave.

140
00:11:03,433 --> 00:11:04,499
Okay.

141
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:09,696
Stop.

142
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:20,640
Do you remember me?

143
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:42,142
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

144
00:11:45,172 --> 00:11:50,133
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

145
00:11:53,182 --> 00:11:59,006
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

146
00:11:59,006 --> 00:12:05,440
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

147
00:12:06,144 --> 00:12:09,957
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

148
00:12:09,957 --> 00:12:14,078
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

149
00:12:14,078 --> 00:12:15,774
♪Open my secret♪

150
00:12:15,774 --> 00:12:21,822
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

151
00:12:21,822 --> 00:12:25,694
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

152
00:12:25,694 --> 00:12:30,200
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

153
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:38,910
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
